{"id":10,"date":"2025-09-05T16:48:44","date_gmt":"2025-09-05T16:48:44","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/?page_id=10"},"modified":"2025-09-05T20:09:59","modified_gmt":"2025-09-05T20:09:59","slug":"about","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/index.php\/about\/","title":{"rendered":"About"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<section id=\"about\" class=\"about-section\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n\n    <!-- Intro -->\n    <h1 class=\"heading\">About Me<\/h1>\n    <p class=\"intro\">\n      I am <strong class=\"highlight1\">Md. Maruf Mullah<\/strong>, a recent graduate in \n      <strong class=\"highlight2\">Mechanical Engineering<\/strong> from the \n      <strong class=\"highlight3\">Military Institute of Science and Technology (MIST)<\/strong>. \n      My academic journey has equipped me with strong fundamentals in mechanical engineering, \n      complemented by hands-on experience in both engineering design and machine learning applications.\n    <\/p>\n\n    <p class=\"intro\">\n      I have worked on projects ranging from <em class=\"highlight4\">CAD\/CAM manufacturing tools<\/em> and \n      <em class=\"highlight5\">Arduino-based prototypes<\/em> to <em class=\"highlight6\">AI-driven software applications<\/em>, \n      showcasing my ability to bridge traditional engineering with modern computational approaches. \n      I also gained practical exposure through industrial training at <strong class=\"highlight7\">IFAD Autos Ltd.<\/strong> \n      and an <strong class=\"highlight8\">MTO Engineer Assessment<\/strong> at <strong class=\"highlight9\">PRAN Group<\/strong>, \n      where I contributed to process mapping, quality control, and productivity improvements.\n    <\/p>\n\n    <p class=\"intro\">\n      Through a blend of academic training, project work, and industry exposure, \n      I continue to develop a versatile profile at the intersection of \n      <span class=\"highlight10\">mechanical systems<\/span> and \n      <span class=\"highlight11\">intelligent technologies<\/span>.\n    <\/p>\n\n    <!-- Research Interests -->\n    <h2 class=\"heading\">Research Interests<\/h2>\n    <div class=\"research-grid\">\n\n      <div class=\"card\">\n        <i class=\"fas fa-cubes\"><\/i>\n        <h3>Materials Science &#038; Engineering<\/h3>\n        <p>Advanced materials, structural properties, and performance optimization.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"card\">\n        <i class=\"fas fa-solar-panel\"><\/i>\n        <h3>Renewable Energy &#038; Sustainability<\/h3>\n        <p>Energy-efficient systems and environmentally conscious technologies.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"card\">\n        <i class=\"fas fa-industry\"><\/i>\n        <h3>Smart Manufacturing<\/h3>\n        <p>AI\/ML for process optimization and intelligent production systems.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"card\">\n        <i class=\"fas fa-project-diagram\"><\/i>\n        <h3>Metamaterials<\/h3>\n        <p>Design and analysis of multifunctional and novel material systems.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"card\">\n        <i class=\"fas fa-robot\"><\/i>\n        <h3>Robotics &#038; AI<\/h3>\n        <p>Integration of AI with robotic systems for autonomy and adaptability.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"card\">\n        <i class=\"fas fa-brain\"><\/i>\n        <h3>Machine Learning in Mechanical Engineering<\/h3>\n        <p>Predictive modeling, simulation, and data-driven decision-making.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"card\">\n        <i class=\"fas fa-water\"><\/i>\n        <h3>Computational Fluid Dynamics (CFD)<\/h3>\n        <p>Numerical modeling and analysis of fluid flow and thermal systems.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"card\">\n        <i class=\"fas fa-atom\"><\/i>\n        <h3>Quantum Computing<\/h3>\n        <p>Exploring emerging computational methods for complex engineering challenges.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<!-- Font Awesome -->\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https:\/\/use.fontawesome.com\/releases\/v5.15.4\/css\/all.css\">\n\n<style>\n  body {\n    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 0;\n  }\n\n  .about-section {\n    padding: 60px 20px;\n    color: #222;\n  }\n\n  .container {\n    max-width: 1100px;\n    margin: auto;\n    padding: 0 20px;\n  }\n\n  .heading {\n    text-align: center;\n    font-size: 2.5rem;\n    color: #34495e;\n    margin-bottom: 30px;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n\n  .heading::after {\n    content: '';\n    display: block;\n    width: 80px;\n    height: 4px;\n    background: #e74c3c;\n    margin: 10px auto 0;\n    border-radius: 2px;\n  }\n\n  .intro {\n    font-size: 1.3rem;\n    line-height: 1.8;\n    margin-bottom: 25px;\n    text-align: justify;\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n  }\n\n  \/* Colorful highlights *\/\n  .highlight1 { color: #e67e22; font-weight: bold; }\n  .highlight2 { color: #1abc9c; font-weight: bold; }\n  .highlight3 { color: #3498db; font-weight: bold; }\n  .highlight4 { color: #9b59b6; font-style: italic; }\n  .highlight5 { color: #f39c12; font-style: italic; }\n  .highlight6 { color: #2ecc71; font-style: italic; }\n  .highlight7 { color: #e74c3c; font-weight: bold; }\n  .highlight8 { color: #8e44ad; font-weight: bold; }\n  .highlight9 { color: #16a085; font-weight: bold; }\n  .highlight10 { color: #c0392b; font-weight: bold; }\n  .highlight11 { color: #2980b9; font-weight: bold; }\n\n  \/* Research Grid *\/\n  .research-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));\n    gap: 30px;\n    margin-top: 40px;\n  }\n\n  .card {\n    background: #f7f9fc;\n    padding: 30px;\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n    text-align: center;\n    transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease, background 0.4s ease;\n    cursor: pointer;\n  }\n\n  .card i {\n    font-size: 3rem;\n    color: #e74c3c;\n    margin-bottom: 15px;\n    transition: transform 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n  }\n\n  .card h3 {\n    font-size: 1.4rem;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n    color: #34495e;\n  }\n\n  .card p {\n    font-size: 1rem;\n    color: #555;\n  }\n\n  \/* Hover Effect *\/\n  .card:hover {\n    transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.03);\n    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n    background: #f1f8ff;\n  }\n\n  .card:hover i {\n    transform: rotate(15deg) scale(1.3);\n    color: #3498db;\n  }\n\n  \/* Responsive *\/\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .intro {\n      font-size: 1.15rem;\n    }\n    .card {\n      padding: 25px;\n    }\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 480px) {\n    .heading { font-size: 2rem; }\n    .intro { font-size: 1.05rem; }\n  }\n<\/style>\n\n<script>\n  \/\/ Animate cards on scroll\n  const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.card');\n  const observer = new IntersectionObserver(entries => {\n    entries.forEach(entry => {\n      if (entry.isIntersecting) {\n        entry.target.style.opacity = 1;\n        entry.target.style.transform = \"translateY(0)\";\n      }\n    });\n  }, { threshold: 0.1 });\n\n  cards.forEach(card => {\n    card.style.opacity = 0;\n    card.style.transform = \"translateY(30px)\";\n    card.style.transition = \"all 0.6s ease\";\n    observer.observe(card);\n  });\n<\/script>\n\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>About Me I am Md. Maruf Mullah, a recent graduate in Mechanical Engineering from the Military Institute of Science and Technology (MIST). My academic journey has equipped me with strong fundamentals in mechanical engineering, complemented by hands-on experience in both engineering design [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-10","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"]